            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:39ed0281-f19e-4c60-900f-a3e7010d76aa</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/manufacturing/~3/pY91VQS0Bzs/manufacturers-survey-trending</link>
