            <title>Brady Announces Shadow Board Sweepstakes</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;img alt="" src="http://media.noria.com/sites/Uploads/2014/7/22/ed6f2701-26d0-4d59-8aab-14cd38fecf5e_Shadow_board.jpeg" style="width: 300px; height: 445px; margin: 7px; float: left;" /&gt;Brady Corp. recently announced its Shadow Board Sweepstakes, offering organizations a chance to win $5,000 in shadow board products and facility services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	The sweepstakes is open to legal residents of the United States who are 18 years of age and older (19 years of age for residents of Alabama and Nebraska) and employed by or own a manufacturing business located within the United States.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	To enter, simply complete the online entry form by Sept. 30, 2014. No purchase is required to enter or win. Limit one entry per person/email address. The grand-prize winner will be selected in a random drawing and awarded $5,000 to be used for Brady shadow boards and services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Brady&amp;#39;s recently released shadow board products are designed to create a visually organized space to store equipment, tools and janitorial supplies, with graphics indicating where tools belong and if anything is missing. In addition to shadow boards, the winning organization can choose from select Brady services, including visual workplace audits, procedure writing, safety training and seminars.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&amp;quot;The Shadow Board Sweepstakes goes far beyond the financial and physical prize options,&amp;quot; said Brady&amp;#39;s Tom Smith. &amp;quot;It helps the winning facility establish the visual and safety solutions needed to have a best-practice, highly efficient workplace. The boards and services are an important step in maintaining effective and streamlined processes to achieve both cost and time savings for years to come.&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	To enter or for the official rules, visit &lt;a href="http://www.BradyID.com/Shadowboard"&gt;www.BradyID.com/Shadowboard&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/manufacturing/~4/iJszVyqALik" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
