            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:240c42fa-02eb-4cb4-a269-a362008c8646</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/manufacturing/~3/-f9IUjPYWgo/nebraska-manufacturing-jobs</link>
