            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:3f098700-6aa8-421d-b9c2-a331008b2f3f</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/manufacturing/~3/sKy3o6LN61s/manufacturers-skills-shortage</link>
