            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:cbc7ff72-8c34-4fdb-b33b-a26f00c64525</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/manufacturing/~3/i6GOIdQeLak/north-dakota-manufacturing</link>
